text: Technically, mai tumhe 6 saalo se jaanti hu. Kota mein Dilip sir ki class ka star ‘Abhinav’, I used to wonder aakhir kaun hai ye abhinav xD. Fir ham college mein mile then ART105 mein. You are a really good person and nice to everyone which I really appreciate. I do wish we could meet again soon.
author: Inshu  Namdev

text:
“ Tu toh bhai hai mera” 
“ Hi Inshu, actually hamlog treasure hunt ke liye team bna rhe and ek insaan ki need aur hai, kya tum available ho?” yehi tha na tera first text to me? 
You are one of those people jinki ek special jagah hai meri life mein. Tere bina college time spend krna bhi impossible sa sound krta. Elections ke time pr tere room ko headquarters banana, wahan RR krna, sir dard hone pr bht saari baat krna. I’m gonna miss all that. 
Tera man na hote hue bhi mere jabardasti krne pr meri HC, Chick Blast ke bahar photos lena, mere saath bahar lunch krne jana — Oh god tere jaise doosra item hai hi nahi is dharti pr. 
Khud sad hone pr bhi doosro ka mood life krne wala, khud tension mein hone pr bhi doosro ke kaam mein help krne wala, hamesha (well most of the time) help krne ke liye ready rhne wala, kahin milega kya mereko koi aur aesa?

Thanks Saini for being there for me and mere sad moments ko happy mein convert krne ke liye as well as happy moments ko aur happy banane ke liye. I would permanently like to subscribe to Saini Friendship policy - 
“Zindagi ke saath bhi and zindagi ke baad bhi” 
Love you bht jyada <3.
author: Inshu  Namdev

text:
Hello Sontu…
Bina padhe marks le aana, pta hona ki har jagah select ho jaega but still rona ki mera toh kahin ni hoga. Tu kaafi talented hai but kabhi kabhi kaafi faltu cheezon mein time barbad kr deta hai (waise ye to sab hi krte) but you should learn to prioritize youself over everything. You’re one of the sweetest people I met on campus. You helped me to deal with my issue and my insecurities. I wish the best for you and would love to go on a walk with you where we can discuss old times and feel nostalgic. You will always be my cute fluffy panda. May we meet soon <3.
author: Inshu  Namdev

text:
Sabse phle to mujhe laga, tera real name hi Amrendra Bahubali hai but with time mujhe sach pta chala xD. You are one of those people jo aero mein bas naam ke liye nahi hain. You did a great job in aero club. Aese hi bakchodi krte rhna, jaldi milte :)
P.S. - next time ped pr se mere liye bhi aam tod lena.
author: Inshu  Namdev

text:
Yo Guptaaaa!!
Saath padhne se lekar saath mein karke ladayi krne ke baad fir se maje krna — aesi journey rahi apan dono ki. 
Mere kaafi dumb se dumb doubts bhi tune bina mereko low feel karaye samjhaye. Apan ne kaafi classes saath mein attend ki and kaafiyon mein toh ham bas baatein hi krte rahe xD.  
I’m really glad ki apan mile but sadly ab tu Mumbai jaa rha and mai nahi! But koi na mai tereko zindagi bhar aese hi faltu sawal puch puch kr tang krte rahungi. 
May we meet again <3.
author: Inshu  Namdev

text: Pta nahi aunty ne kya kha kr paida kiya tha ise — per tootne pr bhi madam ko tennis khelna tha. First year se hi saath rahe apan, saath mein TV room mein PHY and MTH padhe and kaafi time pass kare. I still remember mai kaise tere room ki diwaro pr graffiti banayi thi — Y17 ki tumhari saari best friends ke naam the us diwar pr, maja aata tujhe tang krne mein kaafi. May we meet soon <3 and I want a grand treat from you.
author: Inshu  Namdev

text:
“Kabir to my Aditi” 
I know how special I am in your life and its evidence is dated back to the day when I had my name on your lock screen xD. I have been promoted from your mental support in Robowars to your mental support in real life. Meri tareef kaafi hui chalo ab thodi tareef teri bhi kr deti hu — my first memory of yours is of ART105 — “ Faizan bht achchi photography krta and uske group ki videos bhi kaafi achchi hain” I was like aakhir hai kaun ye and jab mili to Jee result milne ke baad bhi itna disaapointment ni hua jitna tujhse milkar hua.  Vo manhoos ghadi Antaragni ki thi jab hame dono mile. Uske saal ye 4 chaal tujhe kaise jhela, ye to mai hi jaanti hu. 
Biggest perk of being your friend was aunty ke haath ka khana and unka pyaar ( and she loves me more than she loves you ) plus jo tera hai vo mera hai :P
OAT rooftop pr nightout, vo takneek ke time pr NH91 jana, vo unlimited masti — memory loss hone ke baad bhi yaad rakhungi. Thanks for all your gifts and aage bhi aese hi dete rahiyo. 
You will always be the antivirus to my system and no one can take your place. Thanks for always being there for me and fighting for me when I was most vulnerable. Thanks for making me realise my weaknesses and what truly matters in life. I am glad I met you. At last, thoda sa gyan — start treating yourself better. You have been through a lot and deserve a lot of happiness. So stay happy and love you bht jyada <3. Anyway apne ko toh saath hi marna hai so jab tak zinda hain tab tak aese hi tang krti rahungi mai xD
author: Inshu  Namdev

text:
Aero Y17 mein sabse jyada chill rhne wala banda, unofficial branch representative, jiske pass har problem ka solution hai. Aero ke logo ne kaafi nickname rakhe tumhare but Desidaru was  the best. Elections ke time pr kya to Fb pr spam kiya tha xD. 
May we meet soon tab tak ke liye stay happy and tension free.
author: Inshu  Namdev

text: Vo DOAA canteen mein aaloo parathe khate hue Covid discuss krna fir mask lene ke liye bahar campus gate pr jana is the last time I saw you in person. AE ke courses aur labs mein bakchodi krna, those were the good days. Hamesha tension free kaise reh leta hai tu - mereko bhi seekha dena yaar ye. Apni Mumbai to Goa road trip is still pending, uske liye jaldi hi milte.
author: Inshu  Namdev

text:
Yo Manish!

Hamlog sabse phli baar ig third year mein hi mile, elections se phle. Tumhare baare mein kaafi suna tha - president ke topic pr baat ho and tumhara naam na ho ye toh kabhi hua hi nahi but jab mai tumse mili toh maine dekha ki why people believed in you. You have the courage and mindset for leading people and bringing new change so never let that side of yours disappear. There are so many people (including me) on campus who trust you very much and it takes enormous amount of efforts to have that place in someone's life. I really appreciate the caring nature of yours.

You are one of those people who helped me when I was feeling low and encouraged me to do better. I believe it from the bottom of my heart that one day you'll do something big. I'm really glad that we met. I wish hamlog phle mile hote toh kaafi time spend krte saath mein but abhi bhi der nahi hui hai we'll meet soon and bht saari baatein krenge tabtak ke liye stay happy and safe <3
author: Inshu  Namdev

text:
Yo Pence!
Ham ig sabse phle drams mein mile the, kya toh mast time tha jab our only tension was ki kahin senior hamara role na kaat dein xD. Ngl but jab mujhe tumhara naam pta chala toh i was like chalo finally ek insaan hai jiska naam mere naam ki tarah unique hai. Fir hamlog aero mein bhi mile and then SnT too, kaafi kuch common rha. 

I always wanted to tell you that I respect you a lot for the work you have done for the Aerial Robotics team. Kya toh maintain krke rakha tha tumne team ko. I still remember IITR mein kaise tumne team ko lead kiya and motivated the members from time to time. Techmeet ke time your team really made me feel that I was a part of that team. 

I also remember, during my soap box, when people were asking ridiculous questions from me. Though you were supporting someone else and I have no hard feelings about that but what I really appreciated was you were not like those people. Even though you were on the other side, you did what was right. I truly believe you are a man with principles. Be like that always and keep progressing. 

And yes we'll have that deep conversation kabhi na kabhi. Hope we meet again soon.
author: Inshu  Namdev

text:
Heyo Monika! 
you were always a shy type of girl. Apne kaam ke liye credits lene pr itna kaun sharmata hai xD.  I still remember vo robotics ka kaam saath krna and fir midsem ke baad library ke bahar baaki logo ko bolna - "Kitna bhi padlo, tumhara bhi katega" kya to time tha yaar. Hope to meet you soon and logo ka pagal banate <3
author: Inshu  Namdev

text:
Hi Naishu!!
Doaa canteen mein ghanto baatein krna, classes ke time pr baatein krna, fir CCD mein baatein krna - ham kitni baatein krte the xD. Back when you had long hair, Antargni mein kya toh head bang kiya tha. 
It’s been a while since we talked achche se, I was hoping campus mein milenge but sadly vo bhi ni hua. But mai bhi kaafi ziddi hu, jald hi milte <3.
author: Inshu  Namdev

text:
AUV ka kaam krte krte thak jane pr hall 2 canteen jaa kr khana and then saara bill tere account mein likhwana. Hamesha 12 bajne se 10 mins phle Ola book krna and then 12 baje se just ek min phle campus se nikal na — kya to maja aata tha. 
Hamesha kuch toofani krne ke liye ready rhne wala insaan aur mere noob jaise questions ka bina hase answer krne wala friend. Kitna pyara hai rey tu. Location final ho meri, fir BLR mein bhi aese hi backhodi karenge <3
author: Inshu  Namdev

text:
Yo Nilayy

AUV Batti mein mile the apan. Phle mujhe lagta tha ki ye alag padhaku banda hai but jaise time pass hua toh mujhe pta chala ki ye sach ke bilkul close ni hai. Tu hai hi bakchod xD. Kya toh experiments kare hain hamlogo ne AUV room mein, kitne ADC phuke the. Jab bhi mai kahin phas jaati batti ka kaam krte krte toh you were kinda my saviour. But jabse tu AUV se gya apni baat kaafi kam hui hai. I hope hamlog jaldi se mile and wahi same bakchodi karein tab tak ke liye all the best for future and stay happy.
author: Inshu  Namdev

text:
“ Aur Nik free hai? ”

Hamesha hyper active rhne wala, always high on high functional anxiety, faltu ki tension lene wala, ekdm se chid jaane wala still jab bhi mai ek call krti asking for help tu ek dm hazir ho jata, aakhir kya kha kr paida kiya tha aunty ne tereko bey!!

Mera mood kharab hone pr saath mein mama mio jana, internship lagne pr mama mio jana then elections ke time pr mama mio mein ladayi krna, fir mama mio mein hi mere scene create krne pr mereko shaant krna and then back to mujhe chidate rhna, kitna diverse hai tera nature. Tujhe pta hai tu irreplaceable hai isliye beech beech mein nakhre krte rhta hai xD. But jis friendship mein ladayi na ho vo friendship hi kya hai. Apan ladenge marenge but saath rahenge. I wish apan jaldi mile and hall 4 canteen mein baith kr tawa paneer khaye and rant kare ek doosre ke saamne. 

Thanks Tiki! mere itna kuch tujhe bolne pr bhi you always stayed by my side and I’m really grateful for that. Thanks for always having my back and you truly are irreplaceable to me. Love you bht jyada <3.
author: Inshu  Namdev

text:
“ My birthday twin “
First year mein you made classes bearable. Classes end hone pr dhoop mein baith kr chai peena, hamesha yaad rhega mereko. Thanks for listening to all of my rants and mereko samjhane ke liye. 
Har bday pr Hall 10 canteen mein dinner pr jana — apna ek ritual sa ban gya tha. I really wish ki meri location bhi BLR hi ho then apan aese hi naye rituals banaenge apne bday pr. 
I cherish all our memories and hope to create many new ones with you. May we meet soon <3.
author: Inshu  Namdev

text:
Yo PP!

" Chal saath mein assignment krte hain", " Chal saath mein canteen chalte hain", " Chal saath mein exam ke liye chalte hain" - apna aero to saath mein hi nikla hai pura xD!!

I really miss doing assignments with you (mai hi jaanti hu ye online sem mein kaise assignments kiye hain xD). Tu na messenger pr sticker bhejti raha kr mast maja aata tha. I hope apan jaldi se mile and kaafi baatein kare tab tak ke liye stay safe and happy <3. 

P.S. I really liked your Pokémon stuffed toy (please mereko mere bday pr gift krdena vo xD)
author: Inshu  Namdev

text:
Yo pinky xD!!
Hamlog phli baar achche se baat Aero ke freshers pr hi kare the shayad. Uske baad toh kya sahi rha apna baaki 4 saal tak. Classes saath jaana fir saath wapas aana. Subah bina breakfast kare jana then class se aakar saath mein breakfast krna - daily schedule sa ban gya tha apna xD. I still hope ki vo time wapas aaye but sadly we have to keep moving. 
You are really sweet but somewhat naive but I like you the way you are. May we meet again soon <3 tab tak ke liye keep wearing PINK xD
author: Inshu  Namdev

text:
“ Hello Prink”
AE, Robotics club, AUV, SnT Council, the same level of madness — dekh kitna kuch common hai apan dono mein. 
“ Tu hall 12 canteen ka bill dena mai doaa canteen ka pay karungi” 
The first time I met you at the AE Y17 freshers and my first reaction was like “ kitna bhola and chutiya hai ye “ but little did I know ki isi insaan ke saath college ke 4 saal kaatne hain xD. My partner in my ‘ bhookh lag rhi hai chal kuch khaane chalte wala never ending phase ‘. Hamesha mera RR sunte rhna and faltu ka timepass krte rhna. Hamesha bahar jaane and saath mein chill marne ke liye ready rhne wala friend. Vo aero ki classes mein saath baithna and fir prof ke mudne pr hasi control krna fir mere se gaaliyan sun na, kitna time spend kiye apan saath mein. 
Thanks Prink hamesha saath rhne ke liye. I know maine tereko kaafi tang ki hu (ye jhooth hai tho) but tu fir bhi meri hamesha help kiya. 
“ Tu friend nhi parivar hai bc “
P.S. - NIOT ka badla toh lekar rahungi kabhi na kabhi.
author: Inshu  Namdev

text:
According to me, you are the cutest Y17 girl <3.
I still remember Antargni'19 ke time pr when you and Avani were knocking on DIshaa's door like koi emergency hai but then jaise hi door khulta hai tum dono itne bhand the ki bas hase jaa rhe the...ek point pr toh mujhe dar bhi lagne laga tha xD. 
You have a really sweet charisma bas thoda tension kam liya kr. I really felt sometimes ki you were anxious and tensed. You are a pretty woman and ye tension wagera doesn't suit you so just happy and cute. May we meet again <3
author: Inshu  Namdev

text:
Yo Ramola!

Yaar ek meme tha ki 'everyone has a friend whom you always address with their last name that you forget their first name', vo tere pr suit krta ekdm xD. Apan sabse phle drams mein mile the, I found you really funny and it was like tu har role ke liye fit tha. When you started your YT channel, I liked your videos from the start. It was like one of your many hidden talents. Your videos sometimes really made my day during lockdown 2020, thanks for that. 

I am still waiting tere ghar pr aane ke liye so that we can both travel around your place jo ki bht pyara hai <3. May we meet again soon tab take ke liye stay happy and funny just the way you are.
author: Inshu  Namdev

text:
AUV batti mein saath the dunno kab itne achche friends ban gye. AUV mein ladayi krne se lekar ek doosre ke liye best wish krne tak - aesa bipolar nature hai apan dono ka. It was great working with you in AUV, you taught me many things. Thanks for all that. 
May we meet again <3.
author: Inshu  Namdev

text:
Hi Sid Jay,

Kitna time ho gya apni baat hi ni hui. i guess ham log last time tumahre EPFL jaane se phle mile the. You are the sweetest guy at IITK - matlab koi kitna bhi tang krle but you always replied to them sweetly. I still remember hamlog kitna baar CCD mein randomly milte and then kaafi time tak baat bhi karte the. 
I hope we meet again soon and kaafi baat karein tabtak ke liye keep achieving great heights.
author: Inshu  Namdev

text:
Thanya B - my favourite sportsperson on campus. I still remember, how we used to have dinner late at night after coming from our CPAs in the first year, how we used to bitch about people and also, how you used to sit in “dhooop” and drink chai with me. It was a great time that we shared together. Thank you for everything.
May we meet soon <3. 
P.S. - I still want, from the bottom of my heart, to see you in the Olympics one day.
author: Inshu  Namdev

text:
Yo Yashika!

Apna sabse phle ig first year ke vo photoshoot mein mile the. Kya to mast time tha vo. Hamlog fir baaki years mein ig kaafi baar mess mein mile the and mast baatein krte the. I also remember hamlog internship drive ke time pr lift mein mile the and kaise we both were encouraging each other, it was a nice feeling <3. I really appreciate your work ethics. 
May we meet again soon tab tak ke liye stay happy and safe <3
author: Inshu  Namdev
